snippet.title: DC Stays SILENT on Amber Heard as Mera in Fandome 2020
snippet.description:
DC Stays SILENT on Amber Heard as Mera in Fandome 2020
______________________________________________
For more videos subscribe : https://bit.ly/2zoPgqj
______________________________________________
Everyone loved Amber Heard's performance as Mera, Arthur Curry's love interest in james wan's aquaman as the film gained a commercial and critical success it is no surprise that a sequel of the movie was announced with Jason Momoa who is set to return as the DC Comics hero Aquaman 2 will release in december 2022 but there is yet no clarity on Heard's role in the film yet.
